Class ProducaoCientifica

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.ProducaoCientifica

  • @Entity
public class ProducaoCientifica
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    joao_ Class ProducaoCientifica An Entity class for the model designed for a Scientific Paper, journal, book or similar It is mapped in the Database and it has a reference to a "Professor" list, since one or more professors can contribute with the work Its methods are only setters and getters
